:: Lounge [nobr location] {"position":"500,1150","size":"100,100"}
<<set $gamelocation to "Lounge">>

<span> A nice place to rest, relax, and socialize. There are some people mingling around the place. </span>
<br>
<div class="room-hotel">
<<unset $spawnPools>>
<<run setup.refreshFullPool()>>
<<SpawnPoolOnce "fullPool" $fullPool 15>>
<<SpawnRandomNPCs 15>>
<<include "NPC-List">>
</div>

<div id="npcsex-actions-bar">
<<button "Lobby">>
    <<goto "Lobby">>
<</button>>
</div>

